1
00:00:01,040 --> 00:00:06,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The Kingdom of Marinforest is home 
to a human king and three fairy kings.</i></font>

2
00:00:07,620 --> 00:00:11,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Thanks to the Forest Fairy King, 
the land is blessed with abundance,</i></font>

3
00:00:11,520 --> 00:00:13,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and its fertility is guaranteed.</i></font>

4
00:00:14,240 --> 00:00:17,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Thanks to the Sky Fairy King, 
the air is very clean,</i></font>

5
00:00:17,900 --> 00:00:20,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and there is never a shortage 
of life-giving rain.</i></font>

6
00:00:21,080 --> 00:00:23,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Thanks to the Sea Fairy King,</i></font>

7
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:25,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>things like coral, pearls, 
and fish are abundant</i></font>

8
00:00:25,950 --> 00:00:28,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and bring prosperity to the kingdom.</i></font>

9
00:00:28,760 --> 00:00:32,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Everyone in the Marinforest 
royal family is loved by the fairies</i></font>

10
00:00:32,580 --> 00:00:34,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and has received their blessing.</i></font>

11
00:00:35,440 --> 00:00:40,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The fairies' power is vital 
in supporting the kingdom.</i></font>

12
00:00:54,700 --> 00:00:59,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an2}<font color="#3d8afc"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="28"><b><font color="#f76bb3">The Villainess <font color="#6b3e34">Is <font color="#f76bb3">Adored 
<font color="#6b3e34">by the Prince of the Neighbor Kingdom</font></font></font></font></b></font></font></font></font>

13
00:02:13,780 --> 00:02:17,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="TimesNewRoman"><font size="25"><font color="#6b3e34">The <font color="#3d8afc"><b>Mermaid</b> <font color="#6b3e34">Knows Not of <font color="#f76bb3"><b>Love</b></font></font></font></font></font></font></font>

14
00:02:18,730 --> 00:02:21,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll undergo bridal training 
for the next year.</i></font>

15
00:02:22,160 --> 00:02:26,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I do feel a bit sad about 
leaving my homeland.</i></font>

16
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:30,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong, Tiara? 
Is something on your mind?</font>

17
00:02:31,150 --> 00:02:32,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Aqua...</font>

18
00:02:32,770 --> 00:02:36,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I'm very excited to go to Marinforest.</font>

19
00:02:37,220 --> 00:02:40,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure I will miss 
my homeland at times,</font>

20
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:43,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but you'll be with me, so I'll be happy.</font>

21
00:02:43,890 --> 00:02:48,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, honestly... You always 
say such adorable things.</font>

22
00:02:48,970 --> 00:02:51,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If there's ever anything troubling you, 
tell me right away.</font>

23
00:02:51,810 --> 00:02:52,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will.</font>

24
00:02:53,370 --> 00:02:55,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course, if you tell me 
you want to go home,</font>

25
00:02:55,870 --> 00:02:58,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't have the slightest shred 
of confidence that I could let you.</font>

26
00:02:58,750 --> 00:03:00,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Aqua...</font>

27
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:05,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! Is that the border?</font>

28
00:03:05,160 --> 00:03:06,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

29
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:10,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On Lapis Lazuli's side, you can see roses,</font>

30
00:03:10,790 --> 00:03:15,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but on Marinforest's side, 
the border is decorated differently.</font>

31
00:03:18,900 --> 00:03:21,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow! It's incredible!</font>

32
00:03:24,750 --> 00:03:27,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll surprise you even more. Look.</font>

33
00:03:33,010 --> 00:03:36,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So this is the Kingdom of Marinforest!</i></font>

34
00:03:46,870 --> 00:03:50,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the first time 
I've ever seen the ocean!</font>

35
00:03:50,720 --> 00:03:53,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No need to rush. 
The ocean won't run away.</font>

36
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:03,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's Aquasteed and Elliot!</font>

37
00:04:03,010 --> 00:04:05,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome home!</font>

38
00:04:05,850 --> 00:04:07,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How cute!</font>

39
00:04:08,090 --> 00:04:09,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're back.</font>

40
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:12,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have you all been well?</font>

41
00:04:13,170 --> 00:04:15,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to be friends with them, too...</i></font>

42
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:17,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go over there.</font>

43
00:04:17,260 --> 00:04:20,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes, let's. 
Maybe they'll be our friends.</font>

44
00:04:26,460 --> 00:04:27,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good day to you.</font>

45
00:04:27,870 --> 00:04:29,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ew! I hate you!</font>

46
00:04:29,490 --> 00:04:30,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't touch us!</font>

47
00:04:32,190 --> 00:04:34,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fairies are fickle creatures.</font>

48
00:04:34,220 --> 00:04:37,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes, I have heard people say so.</font>

49
00:04:37,550 --> 00:04:39,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who is this?</font>

50
00:04:39,450 --> 00:04:42,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know who! 
They were calling her "Philine"!</font>

51
00:04:42,330 --> 00:04:44,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I like Philine!</font>

52
00:04:46,200 --> 00:04:50,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?! Lady Tiararose is 
<i>far</i> more worthy of your favor!</font>

53
00:04:50,390 --> 00:04:52,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, don't worry about me.</font>

54
00:04:52,440 --> 00:04:56,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I do feel sad that 
they don't like me, though.</i></font>

55
00:04:56,450 --> 00:04:58,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can take your time, Tiara.</font>

56
00:04:58,670 --> 00:05:04,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In fact, I'm actually relieved 
they didn't take you from me.</font>

57
00:05:04,230 --> 00:05:05,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Aqua...</font>

58
00:05:07,870 --> 00:05:08,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

59
00:05:19,420 --> 00:05:23,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Arial"><font color="#e899ce">Icilla Pearllant</font></font></b></font>

60
00:05:19,420 --> 00:05:23,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Arial"><font color="#c5e3e4">Icilla Pearllant</font></font></b></font>

61
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:25,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Icilla?</font>

62
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:26,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

63
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:30,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The sequel's heroine is a duke's 
daughter in Marinforest named Icilla,</font>

64
00:05:30,860 --> 00:05:33,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and just when Prince Aqua 
is feeling fed up with</font>

65
00:05:33,340 --> 00:05:36,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#ffffff">the fiancée the state chose for him, 
he meets her on the seashore!</font></font>

66
00:05:39,260 --> 00:05:43,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Aquasteed, 
it's so good to see you again.</font>

67
00:05:43,150 --> 00:05:45,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, it has been a while.</font>

68
00:05:45,180 --> 00:05:47,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you swim all the way here?</font>

69
00:05:47,400 --> 00:05:51,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I was swimming with the 
sea fairies, and I ended up here.</font>

70
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:55,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome home, Prince Aquasteed.</font>

71
00:05:55,020 --> 00:05:58,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And... this is someone 
I haven't met before, yes?</font>

72
00:05:58,000 --> 00:06:01,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My name is Icilla Pearllant.</font>

73
00:06:01,660 --> 00:06:03,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is my fiancée.</font>

74
00:06:03,860 --> 00:06:05,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh!</font>

75
00:06:05,550 --> 00:06:09,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My name is Tiararose Lapis Clamentile.</font>

76
00:06:09,010 --> 00:06:12,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm very happy to meet you.</font>

77
00:06:12,020 --> 00:06:16,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Pearllants are the ducal family 
that oversees the oceans.</font>

78
00:06:16,590 --> 00:06:21,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Icilla is skilled at raising fish, 
corals, and other things in the sea.</font>

79
00:06:22,180 --> 00:06:25,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She always helps me with my work.</font>

80
00:06:25,030 --> 00:06:27,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I see!</font>

81
00:06:27,310 --> 00:06:30,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll do my best to continue 
to be useful to you!</font>

82
00:06:30,330 --> 00:06:34,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, and please come visit 
our house again soon.</font>

83
00:06:34,760 --> 00:06:38,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I always looked forward to your visits.</font>

84
00:06:38,250 --> 00:06:41,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course. I'll visit soon.</font>

85
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:45,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is it possible that I'm the
villainess in the sequel as well?</i></font>

86
00:06:46,260 --> 00:06:49,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yes, my existence is definitely irregular.</i></font>

87
00:06:49,590 --> 00:06:52,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I might be completely 
removed from the story.</i></font>

88
00:06:53,220 --> 00:06:55,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If I am, then once again...</i></font>

89
00:06:55,510 --> 00:06:59,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me. I'm going to rest 
by the carriage for a bit.</font>

90
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:01,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

91
00:07:09,330 --> 00:07:12,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wasn't expecting the heroine 
to show up so soon.</font>

92
00:07:16,190 --> 00:07:18,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't want to lose Prince Aqua.</i></font>

93
00:07:19,050 --> 00:07:20,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What should I do now?</i></font>

94
00:07:20,770 --> 00:07:23,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What face should I make when I return?</i></font>

95
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:25,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm not confident that I can act cheerful.</i></font>

96
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:27,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How troubling.</font>

97
00:07:27,840 --> 00:07:29,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're troubled?</font>

98
00:07:38,200 --> 00:07:40,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forest... fairies?</font>

99
00:07:44,350 --> 00:07:46,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's your name?</font>

100
00:07:46,340 --> 00:07:50,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, my name is 
Tiararose Lapis Clamentile.</font>

101
00:07:50,620 --> 00:07:52,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tiara! Nice to meet you!</font>

102
00:07:53,170 --> 00:07:55,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love Tiara!</font>

103
00:07:57,860 --> 00:07:59,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't believe it.</font>

104
00:07:59,880 --> 00:08:03,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forest fairies 
don't normally like people,</font>

105
00:08:03,170 --> 00:08:05,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">yet they're blessing her?</font>

106
00:08:05,430 --> 00:08:08,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Elliot? What brings you here?</font>

107
00:08:08,130 --> 00:08:10,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I apologize.</font>

108
00:08:10,490 --> 00:08:13,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been following behind
at a short distance to guard you.</font>

109
00:08:13,880 --> 00:08:17,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you wander out here alone 
because something is wrong?</font>

110
00:08:17,140 --> 00:08:19,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I'm all right.</font>

111
00:08:19,250 --> 00:08:23,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was in the carriage for a long time, 
so I wanted to stretch my legs.</font>

112
00:08:23,470 --> 00:08:25,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tiara, you're not happy?</font>

113
00:08:25,960 --> 00:08:28,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This flower is really tasty!</font>

114
00:08:28,400 --> 00:08:30,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's blessed by the forest fairies!</font>

115
00:08:30,330 --> 00:08:31,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eat it! Eat it!</font>

116
00:08:35,130 --> 00:08:36,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's delicious.</font>

117
00:08:38,110 --> 00:08:40,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She feels better now!</font>

118
00:08:41,280 --> 00:08:42,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tiara!</font>

119
00:08:42,630 --> 00:08:46,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry. I was walking around 
over there a bit.</font>

120
00:08:46,810 --> 00:08:49,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please don't worry me so much.</font>

121
00:08:49,310 --> 00:08:51,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take me with you next time.</font>

122
00:08:51,470 --> 00:08:52,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will.</font>

123
00:08:52,470 --> 00:08:56,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you hungry? 
I brought some sweets with me.</font>

124
00:08:56,550 --> 00:08:58,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I'm all right.</font>

125
00:08:59,060 --> 00:09:01,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm so fortunate.</i></font>

126
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:03,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Instead of being so afraid of the heroine,</i></font>

127
00:09:03,940 --> 00:09:07,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I should treasure all the wonderful 
people who support me.</i></font>

128
00:09:08,570 --> 00:09:10,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Arial"><font color="#74402e">The Castle of Marinforest</font></font></b></font>

129
00:09:11,310 --> 00:09:14,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bet you've never taken such 
a long carriage ride before.</font>

130
00:09:14,900 --> 00:09:16,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you feeling all right?</font>

131
00:09:16,830 --> 00:09:18,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

132
00:09:18,280 --> 00:09:21,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As I mentioned, there'll be 
a welcome party for you in three days.</font>

133
00:09:22,340 --> 00:09:26,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will arrange a dress for you, 
of course, so please wear it.</font>

134
00:09:27,040 --> 00:09:29,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll arrange a dress for me?</font>

135
00:09:29,170 --> 00:09:31,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so happy! Thank you!</font>

136
00:09:35,510 --> 00:09:37,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, darn it all...</font>

137
00:09:37,670 --> 00:09:39,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so adorable.</font>

138
00:09:39,850 --> 00:09:41,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">P-Prince Aqua...</font>

139
00:09:45,300 --> 00:09:47,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A whole year until we're married?</font>

140
00:09:48,250 --> 00:09:52,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's too long. 
I want to make you my wife right now.</font>

141
00:09:53,130 --> 00:09:55,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Aqua, don't be like that.</font>

142
00:09:56,200 --> 00:10:01,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to complete my bridal training 
and be helpful to you as your wife.</font>

143
00:10:01,490 --> 00:10:03,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just wait a bit longer.</font>

144
00:10:04,380 --> 00:10:05,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know.</font>

145
00:10:12,050 --> 00:10:13,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think?</font>

146
00:10:13,480 --> 00:10:17,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I gave you the half-up style that's 
popular in Marinforest right now.</font>

147
00:10:17,510 --> 00:10:19,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's lovely. Thank you.</font>

148
00:10:19,930 --> 00:10:22,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've always been so good 
at doing my hair.</font>

149
00:10:22,910 --> 00:10:25,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is where we encounter a problem.</font>

150
00:10:25,070 --> 00:10:27,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What should we do about a hair accessory?</font>

151
00:10:27,210 --> 00:10:30,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like something that looks 
special for the occasion.</font>

152
00:10:30,130 --> 00:10:33,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case, how about these?</font>

153
00:10:33,370 --> 00:10:36,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They were all picked 
from the castle courtyard.</font>

154
00:10:36,220 --> 00:10:40,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Flowers like these are 
a specialty of Marinforest.</font>

155
00:10:40,040 --> 00:10:42,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're lovely! Aren't they, Philine?</font>

156
00:10:42,650 --> 00:10:45,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I'm sure they'll suit you perfectly.</font>

157
00:10:45,540 --> 00:10:49,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... do you have one 
in a deep blue color?</font>

158
00:10:49,930 --> 00:10:51,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A deep... blue?</font>

159
00:10:51,960 --> 00:10:57,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought it might be nice to wear one
the same color as Prince Aqua's hair.</font>

160
00:10:57,360 --> 00:11:00,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! That's a very good idea!</font>

161
00:11:01,060 --> 00:11:05,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm very sorry, but there are 
no blue flowers this time of year.</font>

162
00:11:05,940 --> 00:11:07,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I see...</font>

163
00:11:14,140 --> 00:11:16,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What could this mean?!</font>

164
00:11:16,040 --> 00:11:18,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It must be a gift from the forest fairies!</font>

165
00:11:19,330 --> 00:11:20,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A gift?</font>

166
00:11:20,490 --> 00:11:24,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. You may be the only one 
in the kingdom right now</font>

167
00:11:24,860 --> 00:11:27,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who's received 
the forest fairies' blessing.</font>

168
00:11:27,460 --> 00:11:31,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are some who are blessed 
by the sea or sky fairies,</font>

169
00:11:31,420 --> 00:11:35,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but we never hear of anyone being 
blessed by the forest fairies.</font>

170
00:11:35,220 --> 00:11:39,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Amazing! Isn't this wonderful, 
Lady Tiararose?</font>

171
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:40,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes!</font>

172
00:12:16,290 --> 00:12:19,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Honestly, my Tiara 
is so adorable, it hurts.</font>

173
00:12:19,930 --> 00:12:20,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

174
00:12:20,900 --> 00:12:24,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those blue roses in your hair 
are beautiful, as well.</font>

175
00:12:24,940 --> 00:12:27,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're the same color as my hair,</font>

176
00:12:27,010 --> 00:12:31,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so it feels as if I'm under the illusion 
that all of you belongs to me.</font>

177
00:12:32,370 --> 00:12:36,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But all of me does belong 
to you, Prince Aqua.</font>

178
00:12:38,660 --> 00:12:42,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am deeply honored to meet you.</font>

179
00:12:42,330 --> 00:12:45,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hope we will enjoy a favorable 
relationship for years to come.</font>

180
00:12:45,240 --> 00:12:50,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Lady Tiararose, Marinforest 
warmly welcomes you.</font>

181
00:12:45,580 --> 00:12:50,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Arial"><font color="#713a36"><font size="16">King of Marinforest</font></font></font></b></font>

182
00:12:45,580 --> 00:12:50,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Arial"><font color="#713a36"><font size="16">King of Marinforest</font></font></font></b></font>

183
00:12:45,580 --> 00:12:50,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Arial"><font color="#a7bce0">Sotiris Marinforest</font></font></b></font>

184
00:12:45,580 --> 00:12:50,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Arial"><font color="#7995c4">Sotiris Marinforest</font></font></b></font>

185
00:12:51,160 --> 00:12:56,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}We are terribly pleased to have 
a lovely young lady like you here.</font>

186
00:12:51,290 --> 00:12:55,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Arial"><font color="#713a36"><font size="16">Queen</font></font></font></b></font>

187
00:12:51,290 --> 00:12:55,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Arial"><font color="#713a36"><font size="16">Queen</font></font></font></b></font>

188
00:12:51,290 --> 00:12:55,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Arial"><font color="#a7bce0">Lavina Marinforest</font></font></b></font>

189
00:12:51,290 --> 00:12:55,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font face="Arial"><font color="#c558bf">Lavina Marinforest</font></font></b></font>

190
00:12:56,590 --> 00:12:59,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You honor me, Your Majesty.</font>

191
00:12:59,500 --> 00:13:02,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will devote myself 
to my studies for the next year</font>

192
00:13:02,300 --> 00:13:05,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">in hopes of supporting
Prince Aquasteed.</font>

193
00:13:05,790 --> 00:13:08,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm so looking forward to 
the future that lies ahead.</i></font>

194
00:13:08,980 --> 00:13:12,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No matter what happens, 
I won't run away this time.</i></font>

195
00:13:12,520 --> 00:13:15,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Aquasteed, Lady Tiararose,</font>

196
00:13:15,820 --> 00:13:18,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">congratulations on your engagement.</font>

197
00:13:18,390 --> 00:13:21,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Lady Icilla.</font>

198
00:13:21,300 --> 00:13:23,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think of Marinforest?</font>

199
00:13:23,700 --> 00:13:26,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you able to live here 
without difficulty?</font>

200
00:13:26,380 --> 00:13:31,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. Prince Aquasteed is taking 
very good care of me, as well.</font>

201
00:13:31,040 --> 00:13:32,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so glad to hear that!</font>

202
00:13:32,970 --> 00:13:36,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I would love to become 
better friends with you.</font>

203
00:13:36,650 --> 00:13:40,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please pay a visit to my home sometime.</font>

204
00:13:40,050 --> 00:13:40,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

205
00:13:40,960 --> 00:13:45,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Icilla's mansion sits next 
to the foremost ocean in Marinforest.</font>

206
00:13:45,800 --> 00:13:48,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure you would love it.</font>

207
00:13:48,750 --> 00:13:50,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I see.</font>

208
00:13:50,750 --> 00:13:53,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I would love to visit sometime.</font>

209
00:13:53,520 --> 00:13:55,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so happy!</font>

210
00:13:55,300 --> 00:13:58,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll show you 
the finest hospitality I can!</font>

211
00:13:58,530 --> 00:14:01,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right. Thank you very much.</font>

212
00:14:01,370 --> 00:14:06,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want to get involved with her, 
but she's moving in quick!</font>

213
00:14:09,910 --> 00:14:13,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#3d8afc"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="24"><b>The Villainess <font color="#6b3e34">Is <font color="#f76bb3">Adored 
by the Prince of the Neighbor Kingdom</font></font></b></font></font></font></font>

214
00:14:19,830 --> 00:14:23,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm actually going to 
visit Lady Icilla now.</i></font>

215
00:14:24,720 --> 00:14:26,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you all right?</font>

216
00:14:26,470 --> 00:14:31,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. I'm sorry to ask this of you, Tarmo.</font>

217
00:14:31,470 --> 00:14:35,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not at all. I am your personal 
knight, Lady Tiararose.</font>

218
00:14:35,560 --> 00:14:37,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are free to ask anything of me.</font>

219
00:14:37,760 --> 00:14:39,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

220
00:14:44,860 --> 00:14:48,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Tiararose, 
thank you for coming to visit!</font>

221
00:14:49,340 --> 00:14:53,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for inviting me, Lady Icilla.</font>

222
00:14:53,250 --> 00:14:57,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please, follow me. 
I'll show you around the garden.</font>

223
00:14:57,100 --> 00:14:58,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

224
00:15:05,130 --> 00:15:09,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, my! I've never seen 
such pretty fish before!</font>

225
00:15:09,760 --> 00:15:13,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The water in this fountain is seawater.</font>

226
00:15:13,300 --> 00:15:18,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These little fish are a rare species 
that only lives in my ocean.</font>

227
00:15:18,770 --> 00:15:21,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's definitely the sequel's heroine.</i></font>

228
00:15:21,030 --> 00:15:22,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Her backstory is solid.</i></font>

229
00:15:23,620 --> 00:15:27,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've prepared tea for you.</font>

230
00:15:27,480 --> 00:15:29,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

231
00:15:32,790 --> 00:15:36,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The ocean is just 
as beautiful as I've heard.</font>

232
00:15:36,250 --> 00:15:39,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you like to try going in it?</font>

233
00:15:39,430 --> 00:15:40,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

234
00:15:40,530 --> 00:15:42,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that's not what I mean!</font>

235
00:15:42,490 --> 00:15:46,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been blessed by the sea fairies,</font>

236
00:15:46,360 --> 00:15:50,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I can use magic that makes 
breathing underwater possible.</font>

237
00:15:50,080 --> 00:15:52,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can even make
a layer of air around your body</font>

238
00:15:52,270 --> 00:15:55,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so you can go in the water 
without getting your clothes wet.</font>

239
00:15:55,460 --> 00:15:57,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can do that?</font>

240
00:15:57,610 --> 00:15:59,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's definitely the sequel's heroine.</i></font>

241
00:15:59,890 --> 00:16:01,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Anything goes.</i></font>

242
00:16:03,150 --> 00:16:06,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Do I stand a chance 
against a kind heroine</i></font>

243
00:16:06,170 --> 00:16:08,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>who's loved by the fairies?</i></font>

244
00:16:08,480 --> 00:16:10,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My father told me</font>

245
00:16:10,610 --> 00:16:14,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that you and Prince 
Aquasteed met at school.</font>

246
00:16:14,690 --> 00:16:15,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

247
00:16:15,540 --> 00:16:19,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you two will be marrying out of love?</font>

248
00:16:19,220 --> 00:16:21,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's wonderful!</font>

249
00:16:21,040 --> 00:16:22,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What does that mean?</i></font>

250
00:16:22,720 --> 00:16:26,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Does Lady Icilla not love Prince Aqua?</i></font>

251
00:16:28,050 --> 00:16:30,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are beautiful yourself, Lady Icilla.</font>

252
00:16:30,550 --> 00:16:33,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aren't you surrounded by men 
who won't leave you alone?</font>

253
00:16:33,380 --> 00:16:37,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Tiararose, please! 
That isn't so at all!</font>

254
00:16:37,610 --> 00:16:42,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have entrusted every aspect 
of my engagement to my father.</font>

255
00:16:42,300 --> 00:16:46,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm happy as long as I can be in the sea.</font>

256
00:16:46,530 --> 00:16:50,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See how beautifully the fish 
and coral have grown?</font>

257
00:16:50,570 --> 00:16:54,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But are there no men 
you've fallen in love with?</font>

258
00:16:54,640 --> 00:16:59,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. It's embarrassing to admit, 
but I've yet to fall in love.</font>

259
00:16:59,290 --> 00:17:02,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It seems hard to believe 
she could be lying.</i></font>

260
00:17:02,500 --> 00:17:05,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How can someone be so pure, 
sweet, and honest?</i></font>

261
00:17:06,300 --> 00:17:08,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you like to go into the ocean now?</font>

262
00:17:08,600 --> 00:17:11,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are so many cute fish there!</font>

263
00:17:11,010 --> 00:17:12,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I'd love to.</font>

264
00:17:15,570 --> 00:17:20,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Grant us your blessing 
to dive into the blue depths.</font>

265
00:17:24,940 --> 00:17:26,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Incredible!</font>

266
00:17:37,360 --> 00:17:40,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They don't even run away from humans?</font>

267
00:17:40,160 --> 00:17:44,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. I'm down here in the ocean every day,</font>

268
00:17:44,170 --> 00:17:46,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I'm friends with the fish.</font>

269
00:17:47,460 --> 00:17:49,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's like a sea goddess.</i></font>

270
00:17:50,510 --> 00:17:52,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The coral is beautiful, too.</font>

271
00:17:52,960 --> 00:17:55,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You make accessories 
and things from it, right?</font>

272
00:17:55,850 --> 00:18:00,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, thankfully, there are 
many who favor our coral products.</font>

273
00:18:00,890 --> 00:18:02,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How wonderful!</font>

274
00:18:04,240 --> 00:18:07,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never dreamed I'd be 
able to walk under the sea.</font>

275
00:18:07,010 --> 00:18:10,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To think there was such a 
beautiful world to be found down here.</font>

276
00:18:10,430 --> 00:18:13,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so glad you're enjoying it.</font>

277
00:18:13,500 --> 00:18:18,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll go back up first 
and prepare some warm tea.</font>

278
00:18:18,120 --> 00:18:21,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I'll go with you.</font>

279
00:18:21,070 --> 00:18:25,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, please, take this opportunity 
to enjoy yourself.</font>

280
00:18:25,180 --> 00:18:27,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The fish are happy you're here, too!</font>

281
00:18:28,160 --> 00:18:30,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, then, I will.</font>

282
00:18:33,400 --> 00:18:36,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It seems like she really 
is a good person.</i></font>

283
00:18:36,530 --> 00:18:38,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And yet, here I was...</i></font>

284
00:18:39,650 --> 00:18:43,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's so pretty. I'm glad I came here.</i></font>

285
00:18:53,340 --> 00:18:54,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Aqua?</font>

286
00:19:06,640 --> 00:19:08,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No... But why?</i></font>

287
00:19:09,360 --> 00:19:11,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is this the power of the game?</i></font>

288
00:19:11,630 --> 00:19:15,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Did I get between 
the two of them after all?</i></font>

289
00:19:16,790 --> 00:19:19,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No! I decided I wouldn't run away!</i></font>

290
00:19:21,330 --> 00:19:24,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This time, I have to make sure 
I get my feelings across!</i></font>

291
00:19:28,830 --> 00:19:31,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tiara, I came to pick you up.</font>

292
00:19:37,000 --> 00:19:40,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please don't leave me alone, Prince Aqua!</font>

293
00:19:43,620 --> 00:19:46,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, it's no use. You're too cute, Tiara.</font>

294
00:19:46,370 --> 00:19:47,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, my!</font>

295
00:19:50,230 --> 00:19:52,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This concludes our tour 
of the castle interior.</font>

296
00:19:52,960 --> 00:19:57,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you like, I could also show you 
the forest behind the castle.</font>

297
00:19:57,120 --> 00:19:59,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Beautiful flowers bloom there.</font>

298
00:19:59,100 --> 00:20:01,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I would love to see it!</font>

299
00:20:02,630 --> 00:20:03,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

300
00:20:07,720 --> 00:20:10,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure they're 
discussing work, as always.</font>

301
00:20:10,630 --> 00:20:12,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But why on the terrace?</i></font>

302
00:20:12,650 --> 00:20:15,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He said he'd be 
in his office all day today.</i></font>

303
00:20:16,100 --> 00:20:19,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See? It looks like they're both 
returning to his office now.</font>

304
00:20:19,860 --> 00:20:22,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So it does. I'm sorry.</font>

305
00:20:23,050 --> 00:20:25,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems I was overthinking things.</font>

306
00:20:27,540 --> 00:20:29,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, my!</font>

307
00:20:29,040 --> 00:20:30,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It really is beautiful!</font>

308
00:20:30,960 --> 00:20:33,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, it's Tiararose!</font>

309
00:20:34,250 --> 00:20:36,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hi, Tiara!</font>

310
00:20:37,210 --> 00:20:40,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello. I see you're 
as energetic as ever today.</font>

311
00:20:42,190 --> 00:20:45,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, I have 
some cookies. Want some?</font>

312
00:20:45,620 --> 00:20:47,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay! I do!</font>

313
00:20:47,350 --> 00:20:49,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're so crispy!</font>

314
00:20:49,510 --> 00:20:52,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yummy! I love them!</font>

315
00:20:52,200 --> 00:20:54,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Th-They're so cute!</i></font>

316
00:20:54,820 --> 00:20:58,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tiara! Over here!</font>

317
00:20:58,590 --> 00:20:59,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

318
00:21:12,290 --> 00:21:14,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The king is up ahead!</font>

319
00:21:14,900 --> 00:21:16,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The king?</font>

320
00:21:22,760 --> 00:21:23,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?!</font>

321
00:21:23,720 --> 00:21:25,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Over here!</font>

322
00:21:27,560 --> 00:21:30,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... Fairy?</font>

323
00:21:40,780 --> 00:21:42,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where am I?</font>

324
00:21:43,660 --> 00:21:45,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you are Tiararose?</font>

325
00:21:48,790 --> 00:21:50,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">King!</font>

326
00:21:50,260 --> 00:21:51,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">King!</font>

327
00:21:54,320 --> 00:21:57,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The king... of the forest fairies?!</i></font>

328
00:23:30,050 --> 00:23:40,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="TimesNewRoman"><font size="25"><font color="#3d8afc"><font color="#f76bb3"><b>Tiara</b> <font color="#6b3e34">in the <font color="#3d8afc"><b>Sleeping Forest</b></font></font></font></font></font></font></font>

329
00:23:30,050 --> 00:23:40,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="TimesNewRoman"><font size="25"><font color="#3d8afc"><font color="#f76bb3"><b>Tiara</b> <font color="#6b3e34">in the <font color="#3d8afc"><b>Sleeping Forest</b></font></font></font></font></font></font></font>

330
00:23:30,780 --> 00:23:34,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The forest fairies love you, 
and you make good cookies?</font>

331
00:23:35,140 --> 00:23:36,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I approve.</font>

332
00:23:36,740 --> 00:23:39,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You may stay in my forest 
as long as you like.</font>

